*gnome-bluetooth-0.7.0 (07 Feb 2006)

  07 Feb 2006; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org>
  gnome-bluetooth-0.5.1-r2.ebuild, gnome-bluetooth-0.6.0.ebuild,
  gnome-bluetooth-0.6.0-r1.ebuild, +gnome-bluetooth-0.7.0.ebuild:
  Version bump (#113497). stable bump for x86 to solve python problems with
  gnome-bluetooth-manager (#99197). version 0.7.0 fixes icon problems
  (#104977).

*gnome-bluetooth-0.6.0-r1 (06 Feb 2006)

  06 Feb 2006; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org> +files/0.6.0-segv.patch,
  +gnome-bluetooth-0.6.0-r1.ebuild:
  revision bump to eliminate a crasher bug (#112217)

  01 Feb 2006; Simon Stelling <blubb@gentoo.org>
  +files/gnome-bluetooth-0.6.0-libdir.patch, gnome-bluetooth-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Fix bug 108880 and 113460; thanks to Octavio Ruiz for providing patches

  22 Dec 2005; John N. Laliberte <allanonjl@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  remove gnome from metadata

  01 Nov 2005; Henrik Brix Andersen <brix@gentoo.org>
  gnome-bluetooth-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Fixed libbtctl version dependency, bug #111096.

*gnome-bluetooth-0.6.0 (28 Oct 2005)

